message:
Git Merge event will be streamed live for those interested. Their official description says: "Git Merge will feature sessions on using Git, scaling Git, and developing on Git from core Git maintainers."

Stream link: https://live-stream.github.com/
story: Ahmed Al-Amir shared a link to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Git Merge 2015 · Git User Conference in Paris, April 8-9 2015
caption: git-merge.com
description: Git Merge will feature sessions on using Git, scaling Git, and developing on Git from core Git maintainers. This April we will be getting together at La Gaîté lyrique in Paris' 3rd arrondissement and wish Git a happy 10th birthday.
